DOC.brief_summary: This is a postmarketing surveillance study in Korea to evaluate the safety and effectiveness of BOTOX® for lateral canthal lines (crow's feet lines) with or without simultaneous glabellar lines.
DOC.brief_title: Safety and Effectiveness of BOTOX® for Lateral Canthal Lines With or Without Simultaneous Glabellar Lines in Korea
DOC.criteria: Subject and Investigator decision to treat crow's feet lines with Botox®
